{"metadata":{"symbolKind":"property","modules":[{"name":"GLib"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Property","extendedModule":"GLib","role":"symbol","externalID":"s:4GLib16DateTimeProtocolPAAE17weekNumberingYearSivp::SYNTHESIZED::s:4GLib11DateTimeRefV","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"weekNumberingYear"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Int"}],"title":"weekNumberingYear"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib","doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/DateTimeRef","doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/DateTimeRef\/DateTimeProtocol-Implementations"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"weekNumberingYear","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si"},{"text":" { ","kind":"text"},{"text":"get","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" }","kind":"text"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This function, taken together with "},{"code":"g_date_time_get_week_of_year()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_date_time_get_day_of_week()"},{"type":"text","text":" can be used to determine the full ISO"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"week date on which "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"datetime"},{"type":"text","text":" falls."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This is usually equal to the normal Gregorian year (as returned by"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"g_date_time_get_year()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"), except as detailed below:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For Thursday, the week-numbering year is always equal to the usual"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"calendar year.  For other days, the number is such that every day","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"within a complete week (Monday to Sunday) is contained within the"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"same week-numbering year."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"For Monday, Tuesday and Wednesday occurring near the end of the year,","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"this may mean that the week-numbering year is one greater than the"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"calendar year (so that these days have the same week-numbering year","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"as the Thursday occurring early in the next year)."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"For Friday, Saturday and Sunday occurring near the start of the year,","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"this may mean that the week-numbering year is one less than the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"calendar year (so that these days have the same week-numbering year","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"as the Thursday occurring late in the previous year).","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An equivalent description is that the week-numbering year is equal to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the calendar year containing the majority of the days in the current"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"week (Monday to Sunday).","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Note that January 1 0001 in the proleptic Gregorian calendar is a","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Monday, so this function never returns 0.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/glib\/datetimeref\/weeknumberingyear"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"abstract":[{"text":"Returns the ISO 8601 week-numbering year in which the week containing","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"datetime","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" falls."}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/DateTimeRef\/weekNumberingYear"},"sections":[],"references":{"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib/DateTimeRef":{"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"DateTimeRef"}],"url":"\/documentation\/glib\/datetimeref","kind":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"DateTimeRef"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/DateTimeRef","title":"DateTimeRef","abstract":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GDateTime"},{"text":" is a structure that combines a Gregorian date and time","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"into a single structure.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic"},"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib":{"kind":"symbol","role":"collection","abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib","title":"GLib","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/glib"},"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib/DateTimeRef/DateTimeProtocol-Implementations":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/DateTimeRef\/DateTimeProtocol-Implementations","role":"collectionGroup","kind":"article","type":"topic","title":"DateTimeProtocol Implementations","url":"\/documentation\/glib\/datetimeref\/datetimeprotocol-implementations","abstract":[]},"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib/DateTimeRef/weekNumberingYear":{"fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"weekNumberingYear","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int"}],"type":"topic","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/glib\/datetimeref\/weeknumberingyear","title":"weekNumberingYear","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Returns the ISO 8601 week-numbering year in which the week containing"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"datetime","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" falls."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/DateTimeRef\/weekNumberingYear"}}}